Package: foldercloud
Type: Package
Title: Loads Pdfs From a Folder and Creates a Wordcloud
Version: 1.1
Author: James Conigrave
Maintainer: James Conigrave <james.conigrave@gmail.com>
Description: Contains a single function 'foldercloud'. This function loads the contents of all PDFs in a folder. It then cleans the data and turns it into a wordcloud of frequencies.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
